In this newsletter: Wednesday June 5 (before a ”red” holiday) MONDAY BAR + TECHTRIBE present: ELECTRIC CAFÉ • Belgian super duo JOYHAUSER + Swedish psy legend TICON + more • An amazing new, central venue with Monday Bar style production • Online tickets at Billetto and cheaper cash-only at C.U.M. Clubwear Friday-Sunday September 20-22: MONDAY BAR presents: THE 2024 CRUISE (no 61) • 2 night cruise to Tallinn, Estonia (41 hrs) • All cabins are booked, but there’s still room to upgrade if you are only 1-3 ppl in a cabin • 17 djs presented so far. The rest of the lineup will be announced weekly FUTURE LOUNGE: DO YOU WANT TO PLAY ON THE 2024 SEPTEMBER CRUISE? • Send in a 60-minute mix to us • Info in both Swedish and English Dear Monday Bar family, Today marks only 3 weeks until our latest project, ELECTRIC CAFÉ at Biblioteket Live in central Stockholm on June 5 featuring Belgian super duo JOYHAUSER and Swedish TICON. We’re expecting a full house and tickets are available bot online at Billetto and cheaper cash-only tickets at C.U.M. Clubwear. All cabins are now SOLD OUT, but there is still capacity to fill booked cabins with more people (up to 4 persons per cabin in standard A, B and E class). So if you know someone who have booked only 1, 2 or 3 persons in one cabin, they should be able to get an upgrade for an extra fee. You should speak to the booking office about this and have your booking reference ready. Call +46-8-666 33 33 or send an email to: kundservice@tallinksilja.com The international lineup for the September cruise will soon be complete. We have so far presented 17 djs on our social media and homepage, and will continue to present the rest weekly during spring and early summer. Future Lounge Regarding the rest of the lineup, we have decided to run the popular Future Lounge concept again, meaning that we give new, not yet established DJs a chance to play on a dedicated dance floor, this time on at the daytime party on Saturday. See more info below, both in Swedish and English. Monday Bar crew 🥰 TICKETS  <https://billetto.se/e/electric-cafe-feat-joyhauser-ticon-more-biljetter-974824> FACEBOOK EVENT  <https://www.facebook.com/events/312160874923600> ****** In Swedish (English below) ****** FUTURE LOUNGE - VISA HUR DET SKA LÅTA! Vill du spela 60-90 minuter på The 2024 Cruise 20-22 September? Skicka in en mix till oss senast lördag 15 juni På denna kryssning hade vi tänkt att köra det populära Future Lounge-konceptet igen, dvs vi ger nya, icke ännu etablerade djs chansen att spela på ett dedikerat dansgolv, denna gång dagsfesten högst upp i fartyget på lördag eftermiddag. Känner du för att prova lyckan och spela här, skicka in en mix till oss på max en timme till någon av nedanstående adresser (mejla, länka eller cd) innan lördag 15 juni. Vi vill gärna ha alla typer av elektronisk dansmusik som techno, trance, psy, progressive, hardstyle, drum’n’ bass mm (dock ej de mest extrema stilarna som hardcore uptempo mm). Sedan lyssnar vi på alla bidrag och väljer ut ett antal djs i olika genrer som kommer att få spela på kryssningen. DETTA GÄLLER Skicka in en mix till Future Lounge-golvet senast lördag 15 juni. GLÖM INTE att berätta vad du heter, ditt dj-namn samt kontaktuppgifter (email, Facebook + mobil). Berätta gärna kortfattat om dig själv och vilken musik du spelar. BOKA HYTT SJÄLV För att få spela måste du ha bokat hyttplats själv men du kommer att få värdekuponger för 1000 kr som kan användas både för dryck och mat på kryssningen. Var och en som vi väljer ut kommer att få spela 60-90 minuter på Future Lounge-golvet på en tid som vi väljer. Lägg gärna upp mixen på t ex Mixcloud och mejla länken till oss. https://www.mixcloud.com/ <https://www.mixcloud.com/> Mejla ditt bidrag till: future@mondaybar.com <mailto:future@mondaybar.com> Om du skickar en fil, använd gärna WeTransfer: https://wetransfer.com <https://wetransfer.com/> Till: future@mondaybar.com <mailto:future@mondaybar.com> Det går även att skicka en CD till: Future Lounge c/o Monday Bar Högbergsgatan 18 116 20 Stockholm ***** In English ***** FUTURE LOUNGE - SHOW US HOW IT SHOULD SOUND! Would you like to play 60-90 minutes on The 2024 Cruise, September 20-22? Send us a mix no later than Saturday June 15. On this cruise we are planning to run the popular Future Lounge concept again, meaning that we give new, not yet established DJs a chance to play on a dedicated dance floor, this time at the daytime party on the ship's ”Disco Ibiza” on deck 10 Saturday afternoon. If you feel like to trying your luck and play here, send us a DJ mix of a maximum 60 minutes to one of the addresses below (email, file/web transfer or CD) before Saturday June 15. We’re looking for all types of electronic dance music such as techno, trance, psy, progressive, hardstyle, drum'n 'bass, etc (however, not the really extreme styles such as harcdcore uptempo) We will listen to all mixes and select a number of DJs in different genres who will be given the opportunity to play on the cruise. HERE’S HOW IT WORKS Send us a mix to the Future Lounge floor by Saturday, June 15. DON’T FORGET to include your name, your DJ name and contact information (email, Facebook + mobile). And also please tell us briefly about yourself and what music you play. BOOK THE CABIN YOURSELF If you are selected, you need to book a cabin by yourself, but you will receive vouchers for SEK 1,000 that can be used for both drinks and food on the cruise. Each one we select will be allowed to play 60-90 minutes on the Future Lounge floor at a time of our choosing. A good idea is to put up your mix on Mixcloud and then email the link to us. Email your contribution to: future@mondaybar.com <mailto:future@mondaybar.com> If you are sending a file transfer, please use WeTransfer: https://wetransfer.com <https://wetransfer.com/> To: future@mondaybar.com <mailto:future@mondaybar.com> You can also send a CD by snail mail to: Future Lounge c/o Monday Bar Högbergsgatan 18 116 20 Stockholm TICKETS  <htt